## Audit

- Track who/when on journal post; avoid silent UPDATE/DELETE of posted ledger rows.

## Multi-entity (this app)

- Filter by entity/organization on reports and journal queries — never return cross-entity data without explicit scope.

## Python migration path

When adding Python services here, use FastAPI + async SQLAlchemy + PostgreSQL + Pydantic v2 and enforce tenant RLS in migrations.
